{"tid":2171742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社工涉拒出示身份證被控 女督察認要警展示委任證不屬阻差辦公","createTime":"2020-08-24T07:11:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T08:40:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4aa04a098c0f48cfb0b365f3a43a4cdeb037c387","tid":2171742,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:11:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">女督察梁敏儀</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5BH2Ols1wG_Zw9FPlGBoYj-nkY8=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3TBXLPT7YJFAFPCZOVZCEZJW7A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5BH2Ols1wG_Zw9FPlGBoYj-nkY8%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3TBXLPT7YJFAFPCZOVZCEZJW7A.JPG&h=0f04cfcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年8月25日網民發起荃葵青遊行，最後爆發警民衝突，警方拘捕多人。當日有女社工疑因拒絕出示身份證，並要求身穿防暴裝的女督察展示委任證，因而被控阻差辦公罪，案件今開審。女督察今指自己當時身穿防暴裝，女社工要她出示委任證，實屬不合理。辯方指案中是因女督察拒絕出示委任證，才會阻撓她本人執行職務，亦指當時其實有其他警員向被告出示委任證。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/CUKU4YA4HVENVN5ABU6PKEBVEM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FCUKU4YA4HVENVN5ABU6PKEBVEM%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=7abb31e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FCUKU4YA4HVENVN5ABU6PKEBVEM%2F&h=424a2805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/CUKU4YA4HVENVN5ABU6PKEBVEM/</a>"},{"pid":"50506c76abe234cfa1d8f19c41ef984c688ca58f","tid":2171742,"uid":49329,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:14:26.000Z","msg":"黑警死全家"},{"pid":"9e62cd00f9eeed127831e61b0576f56f95efa08a","tid":2171742,"uid":363990,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"50506c76abe234cfa1d8f19c41ef984c688ca58f","tid":2171742,"uid":4